title: Elvis Presley Live Music Videos
description:
31 Clips with Elvis Presley. Live performances, bloopers and a 7 minute Press Conference the Hilton ( New York June 9,1972). Mixed AVI and MPG files. If you can't get a file to play on Win media player, download the free VLC player at http://www.videolan.org/vlc/  It will play every video in the pack. Remember that you can download separate videos/files from the torrent. Enjoy =)
